Scientific-Atlanta, he is. As president and chief executive,
McDonald has pushed this maker of television equipment to chase the
promise of digital interactive TV that glimmers on a distant
horizon. (Haddad, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   LATE-FLIGHT _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ Of all the flights to all
the airports across America, Delta's late-night hop from Atlanta to
West Palm Beach distinguished itself in the most irritating way.
First, it made the federal Department of Transportation's List of
Shame, which ranks domestic flights that arrive late more than 80
percent of the time. It finished 1997 with the very worst on-time
record of any flight by the 10 major airlines required to file
reports. Then The Wall Street Journal _ factoring in crowding,
breakdowns, stomach-churning snacks and other miseries of the skies
_ pronounced it one of the 5 Worst Flights in America. How bad can
any less-than-two-hour flight be? Climbing aboard was the only way
to find out. (Kalajian, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   MONEYTALK-COLUMN _ Post-holiday letdown gives a lot of people
the blahs. But it can also be a breather and a time to look ahead.
Most of us have some time off this week, or at least a slack period
at work. Most of us have been partying, spending and generally
going at warp speed for weeks now. And almost all of us suffer from
nagging suspicions that things have gotten complicated, expensive
and a little bit out of control. One way to recover is to try to
get a grip on your financial life. With a little organization and
effort, you can begin to recoup some feeling of control over your
financial life. (Ezell, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
