</P>
<P>
   Maybe too, sweet reason will also descend on the shoulders of
these latter, despite the atrocities and humiliations heaped upon
them by Belgrade. And then again, 1999 may be when Saddam Hussein
makes a state visit to Washington. &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL; 
</P>
<ANNOTATION>
    &UR; (STORY CAN END HERE AT 625. OPTIONAL MATERIAL FOLLOWS) &LR;  &QC; 
</ANNOTATION>
 &LR;  &QL;
