</P>
<P>
   It would guarantee the essentials: the Kosovo Albanians would be
freed from the threat of Serbian oppression and violence; the Serbs
would be assured of access to their holy sites, political and
religious.
</P>
<P>
   Above all, it would buy time, to wait out Slobodan Milosevic. &QL; 
