<HEADER>
A0927 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-OLY-BRIBERY     12-29 0033
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-OLY-BRIBERY-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   OLY-BRIBERY (Washington) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Dec. 29. &QL;
</P>
