<P>
   (NYT13) NEW YORK -- Dec. 29, 1998 -- SCULPTURE-FLOATER, 12-29 --
Visitors to the Duane Hanson exhibit at The Whitney Museum take a
close look at one of the realistic sculptures on Tuesday. A vast
floor at the museum has been sparsely populated by Hanson's
minutely detailed sculptures of average Americans. (Sara
Krulwich/New York Times Photo) *LITE
</P>
<P>
   (NYT12) UNDATED -- Dec. 29, 1998 -- SMALL-CARS, 12-29 -- The
