<HEADLINE>
BUSINESS TRAVEL: DELTA'S BUSINESS ELITE CLASS; MARRIOTT IN MOSCOW;
FITNESS AT PENNSYLVANIA AIRPORTS; STARWOOD'S FREQUENT-GUEST
PROGRAM; DELAY IN IRS RULE CHANGE 
